metadata.description: 3333Genesis is an exclusive collection consisting of 3333 non-fungible tokens designed by a team of visual artists. The purpose of this collection is twofold.On the one hand, it constitutes a key step in introducing the DarkadeNFT Universe to the public and generating interest in users and investors.On the other hand, it rewards all those who decide to believe in the project and to actively participate with important bonuses, rewards and permanent benefits once the Crafting Chronicles game is launched.
metadata.name: Darkade Mistery
